Theyâ€™re here!!! We are so excited @catalpastudio to begin our transition to using biodegradable/ compostable tattoo supplies, starting with biodegradable gloves from the excellent Toronto- based @goodjudy.ca. In the coming months we look forward to replacing our razors and plastic hygienic products with biodegradable razors and barrier film.
Other goals to reduce the waste we produce at Catalpa:
-donate paper scraps to a local paper making company
-turn our full page paper waste into hand-made books
-using compostable garbage bags
Other actions we are taking to support climate justice:
-starting this week there will be â€œPerverts Against Pipelinesâ€ t-shirts for sale in our little boutique. All profits from their sales will go to the Unistâ€™otâ€™en Legal Defence fund which needs our support more than ever.
